column2: Experienced (>20 years of experience) commodity trader
Proven success working in the petrochemical industry (polyolefins and oil derivatives) in very volatile developing markets (Eastern Europe, CIS countries, Middle Asia)
Extensive multifunctional experience (IT, finance, supply chain, marketing, distribution build-up)
Solid records in building an “end-to-end” value chain from the source to end consumers
An adept negotiator with exceptional organizational and analytical abilities.
A motivating leader with superior communication skills. Value diversity and comfortably manage cultural differences in complex matrix organizations.
